  <data name="GamePage_DLSSPresetInfo_Message" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>DLSS presets are contained within DLSS DLL files contained within your games install directory. Different DLSS DLLs have different presets. For example preset K was not introduced until DLSS v310.2. So if you use DLSS v3.7 and you set preset to K it will not use preset K and instead it will fallback to whatever preset the game chooses to use.

The same applies to global presets. If you select preset K but your game uses DLSS v3.7 you will not be using preset K and instead the game will fallback to whatever its default is.

To verify what preset is being used please enable the DLSS on-screen indicator.</value>
